Sentencas: Reducing the operating temperature is the developing trend for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The key is to develop the cathode with high electrocatalytic activity for oxygen reduction reaction operated at reduced temperatures.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ba-deficient Ba1 - xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3 - delta (Ba1 - xBCN, 0 <= x <= 0.10) are synthesized by solid-state reaction method and evaluated as novel cathodes for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ba1 - xBCN is preserved to primitive cubic perovskite phase and meets the compatibility requirement with gadolinium doped ceria oxide (GDC) electrolyte at 950 degrees C.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Though the Ba deficiency distorts the cell symmetry, it improves the charge transfer steps rapidly, ascribing to the improvement of oxygen vacancy concentration.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization resistance of Ba0.95BCN is as low as 0.056 omega cm(2) in air at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density of the single cell with this cathode is as high as 1.41 W cm(-2) at 750 degrees C with wet H-2 as fuel and air as oxidant, indicating the great potential for enhanced performance of Co-based cathodes with A-site deficiency.
Titulo: Promotion on electrochemical performance of Ba-deficient Ba1- xBi0.05Co0.8Nb0.15O3- δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
